[CLS] [SEP] ( CNN)Paul Walker is hardly the first actor to die during a production . [CLS] [SEP] But Walker 's death in November 2013 at the age of 40 after a car crash was especially eerie given his rise to fame in the " Fast and Furious " film franchise . [CLS] [SEP] The release of " Furious 7 " on Friday offers the opportunity for fans to remember -- and possibly grieve again -- the man that so many have praised as one of the nicest guys in Hollywood . [CLS] [SEP] He was a person of humility , integrity , and compassion , " military veteran Kyle Upham said in an email to CNN . [CLS] [SEP] Walker secretly paid for the engagement ring Upham shopped for with his bride . [CLS] [SEP] " We did n't know him personally but this was apparent in the short time we spent with him . [CLS] [SEP] I know that we will never forget him and he will always be someone very special to us , " said Upham . [CLS] [SEP] The actor was on break from filming " Furious 7 " at the time of the fiery accident , which also claimed the life of the car 's driver , Roger Rodas . [CLS] [SEP] Producers said early on that they would not kill off Walker 's character , Brian O'Connor , a former cop turned road racer . [CLS] [SEP] Instead , the script was rewritten and special effects were used to finish scenes , with Walker 's brothers , Cody and Caleb , serving as body doubles . [CLS] [SEP] There are scenes that will resonate with the audience -- including the ending , in which the filmmakers figured out a touching way to pay tribute to Walker while " retiring " his character . [CLS] [SEP] At the premiere Wednesday night in Hollywood , Walker 's co - star and close friend Vin Diesel gave a tearful speech before the screening , saying " This movie is more than a movie . " [CLS] [SEP] " You 'll feel it when you see it , " Diesel said . [CLS] [SEP] " There 's something emotional that happens to you , where you walk out of this movie [CLS] [SEP] and you appreciate everyone you love because you just never know when the last day is you 're gon na see them . [CLS] [SEP] " There have been multiple tributes to Walker leading up to the release . [CLS] [SEP] Diesel revealed in an interview with the " Today " show that he had named his newborn daughter after Walker . [CLS] [SEP] Social media has also been paying homage to the late actor . [CLS] [SEP] A week after Walker 's death , about 5,000 people attended an outdoor memorial to him in Los Angeles . [CLS] [SEP] Most had never met him . [CLS] [SEP] Marcus Coleman told CNN he spent almost $ 1,000 to truck in a banner from Bakersfield for people to sign at the memorial . [CLS] [SEP] " It 's like losing a friend or a really close family member ... even though he is an actor and we never really met face to face , " Coleman said . [CLS] [SEP] " Sitting there , bringing his movies into your house or watching on TV , it 's like getting to know somebody . [CLS] [SEP] It really , really hurts . [CLS] [SEP] " Walker 's younger brother Cody told People magazine that he was initially nervous about how " Furious 7 " would turn out , but he is happy with the film . [CLS] [SEP] " It 's bittersweet , but I think Paul would be proud , " he said . [CLS] [SEP] CNN 's Paul Vercammen contributed to this report .